@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_frvmmp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.61
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.77)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.48)) + (0.02 - (v1 + 0.54 - tmp + 0.85)))
    data[tid] = v0
